headline: Fifth Third and Eldridge Announce Private Credit Partnership
summary: CINCINNATI, July 29, 2025--Fifth Third Bancorp (NASDAQ: FITB) and Eldridge today announced a strategic partnership to offer private credit arrangements to Commercial Bank clients. This program is built to enhance the ability for both parties to meet emerging and evolving needs and provide reliable private credit solutions to clients.
